our event...\" rows=\"6\"></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Inquiry</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Elegance Events. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Optional: Add subtle animations or interactions here if needed\n        // For this elegant design, we'll keep it minimal.\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}